{"tid":2488817,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬前軍官：倘爆內戰料多人變節","createTime":"2021-04-14T13:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T13:46:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc74ca6fc199e28024a1e9a6e7d5a165ec7abeec","tid":2488817,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210414/GHWEVWF5NJFF5IS6TZCOACOVVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210414%2FGHWEVWF5NJFF5IS6TZCOACOVVQ%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvpvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=4280d578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210414%2FGHWEVWF5NJFF5IS6TZCOACOVVQ%2F&h=1cf29024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210414/GHWEVWF5NJFF5IS6TZCOACOVVQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n緬前軍官：倘爆內戰料多人變節<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yYjL_Ke3qphXrsBSETkeEoLaUPE=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TQTPSBZCCBASVKL52OFK47PRRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyYjL_Ke3qphXrsBSETkeEoLaUPE%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTQTPSBZCCBASVKL52OFK47PRRQ.jpg&h=966b2523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■土瓦昨有一批示威者在潑水節持鮮花反抗軍政府暴行。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸反軍方政變至今，逾700名民眾被殺。有變節軍人表示，軍隊內其實有四分三人知道自己正做錯事，但不敢以下犯上，又估計一旦爆發內戰，會有更多軍人變節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n75%軍人知錯不敢反抗<br />\n<br />\n林泰昂上尉是其中一名變節的低級軍官，他向自由亞洲電台表示：「我認為75%或更多軍人知道他們做的是錯事，但他們擺脫不了&hellip;&hellip;軍人被灌輸『平民是恐怖分子』，大部份人都知道不公平，但無人敢說真話。」對於多個少數民族武裝組織表明會與軍方抗衡，有可能爆發戰爭，他估計若各組織團結起來，軍方會有更多人變節，認為「只有少數士兵會拼死守衞他們的小隊」。<br />\n<br />\n各地衝突本周持續。當地傳媒指，實皆省城市德穆前日有軍人闖入一間醫院毒打兩名職員，並用槍指嚇醫生和護士，要求他們交出手機。城內多處部署了狙擊手，又有無人機在上空監察。軍事組織克倫民族聯盟則稱，軍方上周曾於三日內十次派軍機到聯盟控制區。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸新年假期昨日開始，很多民眾都沒有慶祝，改為上街示威，捧着傳統的潑水節花盆向極權宣洩不滿。有網民坦言「我們不享受這一年，只會在得到民主後才慶祝」。<br />\n<br />\n英國 《泰晤士報》/《緬甸當下》/路透社"},{"pid":"5fd3282896f183a1f2152a046f672c42bd7b5cc7","tid":2488817,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca8d6c17df29009adf6ef3a94802b303c5e86d9","tid":2488817,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8229fceab756c218eebad9c214edcd949c53f40","tid":2488817,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"當年都好多人話會有白警"},{"pid":"e0b440aaa567fc5bcb4c9f63c089a5ad09a4cb00","tid":2488817,"uid":54623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"香港內戰<br />\n唯一出路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e4bee4c2598004adcfa9f3e40bb11e15fe3976","tid":2488817,"uid":54623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8229fceab756c218eebad9c214edcd949c53f40","tid":2488817,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"當年都好多人話會有白警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:40:43.000Z","msg":"Forgiveness is between them and god.It's my job to arrange the meeting."},{"pid":"98f257f261c7520a1730d1d1afeb4831cd11b110","tid":2488817,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"軍隊內其實有四分三人知道自己正做錯事<br />\n<br />\n即係如果開始變節,緬甸人民會反cup <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ba0ef7ab006fd3c3d1beba0cee8b266f52b2f8","tid":2488817,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"以武制暴"},{"pid":"bd8507e3cf2978aee8391cf4ca71e32aec40b1fe","tid":2488817,"uid":8948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8229fceab756c218eebad9c214edcd949